sequenceDiagram
    participant Operator as TrustyAI LMEval Operator
    participant Pod as LMEval Pod<br/>(Batch Job)
    participant EvalHub as EvalHub Service<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant HF as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Inference as Inference Endpoint<br/>(vLLM/TGI)<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
    participant OCI as OCI Registry (Quay)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant MLflow as MLflow Server<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Operator,Pod: Flow 1: Standard Evaluation Job

    Operator->>Pod: Create K8s Job<br/>(from LMEvalJob CR)
    activate Pod

    Pod->>EvalHub: POST status: INITIALIZING<br/>Auth: Bearer Token<br/>TLS 1.2+
    Pod->>HF: GET datasets & tokenizer<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (HF_TOKEN)<br/>TLS 1.2+
    HF-->>Pod: Benchmark data

    Note over Pod,Inference: Core Evaluation Loop

    loop For each benchmark task prompt
        Pod->>Inference: POST /v1/completions<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (OPENAI_API_KEY)<br/>TLS 1.2+ (custom CA supported)
        Inference-->>Pod: Model completions + logprobs
    end

    Pod->>EvalHub: POST status: POST_PROCESSING<br/>Auth: Bearer Token<br/>TLS 1.2+

    Pod->>OCI: Push OCI artifact (via skopeo)<br/>Auth: Docker auth config<br/>TLS 1.2+
    Pod->>MLflow: POST evaluation metrics<br/>TLS 1.2+

    Pod->>EvalHub: POST status: COMPLETED<br/>+ evaluation results<br/>Auth: Bearer Token<br/>TLS 1.2+

    deactivate Pod

    Note over Operator,S3: Flow 2: Offline / Air-Gapped Evaluation

    Operator->>Pod: Create K8s Job<br/>(offline=true)
    activate Pod

    Note over Pod,S3: Init Container Phase
    Pod->>S3: Download datasets & tokenizers<br/>Auth: AWS IAM credentials<br/>TLS 1.2+ (custom CA)
    S3-->>Pod: Test data → /test_data

    Note over Pod: HF_HUB_OFFLINE=1<br/>HF_DATASETS_OFFLINE=1<br/>TRANSFORMERS_OFFLINE=1

    Pod->>Pod: Load data from /test_data<br/>(local filesystem)

    loop For each benchmark task prompt
        Pod->>Inference: POST /v1/completions<br/>Auth: Bearer Token<br/>TLS 1.2+
        Inference-->>Pod: Model completions
    end

    deactivate Pod
